high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk forward to face the trash can.
Pick up the potato in the trash can.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the trash can.
Place the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the fridge, then turn around and look at the recycle bin on the floor.
Take the potato out of the recycle bin.
Turn around and veer right to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Turn around and veer right again back to the recycle bin.
Place the potato in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato in a garbage bin.

high_descs: Turn left then walk straight to the wall and then turn right to face the kitchen counter
Pick up the potato from the bottom of the green trash bin
Turn left and walk straight slightly then turn left and walk up to the microwave
Place the potato in the microwave and heat then remove the potato
Turn left then walk straight to the wall and then turn right to face the kitchen counter
Place the potato in the bottom of the green trash bin
anns.task_desc: Microwave a potato from the green trash bin
